<h2>Manage milestones, updates and successes</h2>

<p>The Milestones, Updates and Successes section provides a comprehensive view of project progress tracking, including milestones, monthly updates, and weekly success stories.</p>

<h3>Overview page</h3>
<p>The overview page shows summary counts and status for:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Milestones:</strong> Total, active, completed, and overdue milestones</li>
    <li><strong>Monthly Updates:</strong> Complete, due, and late submissions</li>
    <li><strong>Weekly Successes:</strong> Total successes and this week's count</li>
</ul>
<p>You can access the overview by navigating to your project and selecting <strong>Milestones, updates and successes</strong> from the project navigation menu.</p>

<h3>Milestones</h3>
<p>Milestones track key deliverables and checkpoints in your project:</p>
<ul>
    <li>View all milestones in a sortable table</li>
    <li>See status (complete, at risk, in progress, delayed)</li>
    <li>Track due dates and actual completion dates</li>
    <li>Monitor progress percentage</li>
    <li>Click on a milestone to view detailed information and updates</li>
</ul>
<p>To add a milestone, click <strong>Add milestone</strong> from the milestones view.</p>

<h3>Monthly updates</h3>
<p>Monthly updates are required submissions that must be completed by the 5th working day of the following month (configurable by administrators):</p>
<ul>
    <li>View all monthly periods starting from November 2025</li>
    <li>See due dates and submission status (upcoming, due, late, or submitted)</li>
    <li>Add or edit updates for each month</li>
    <li>Track which periods have been completed</li>
</ul>
<p>To add a monthly update:</p>
<ol>
    <li>Navigate to the <strong>Monthly Updates</strong> view</li>
    <li>Find the period you want to update</li>
    <li>Click <strong>Add Update</strong> for that period</li>
    <li>Enter your narrative update</li>
    <li>Submit the update</li>
</ol>

<h3>Weekly successes</h3>
<p>Weekly successes allow you to record positive outcomes and achievements on a weekly basis:</p>
<ul>
    <li>View all weekly success updates</li>
    <li>See which week each success relates to</li>
    <li>Track who recorded each success</li>
    <li>Mark successes as reported to SLT (Senior Leadership Team)</li>
    <li>View legacy successes (older successes not linked to specific weeks)</li>
</ul>
<p>To add a weekly success:</p>
<ol>
    <li>Navigate to the <strong>Weekly Successes</strong> view</li>
    <li>Click <strong>Add weekly success</strong></li>
    <li>Select the week and enter the success description</li>
    <li>Optionally mark as reported to SLT</li>
    <li>Save the success</li>
</ol>

<h3>Navigation</h3>
<p>The section uses an expandable navigation menu. When you select <strong>Milestones, updates and successes</strong>, you'll see sub-menu options for:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Overview:</strong> Summary dashboard with counts and status</li>
    <li><strong>Milestones:</strong> Detailed milestone tracking</li>
    <li><strong>Monthly Updates:</strong> Monthly update management</li>
    <li><strong>Weekly Successes:</strong> Success story tracking</li>
</ul>

